title: International Khiladi
subTitle: An international crime boss and his journalist girlfriend fall victim to an elaborate conspiracy that claims an innocent life and turns them into bitter enemies.

title: Insaniyat Ke Devta
subTitle: Two friends, Balbir and Anwar, join forces to defeat an influential tycoon who wishes to destroy an ashram and use the property to further his own selfish purposes.

title: Khudgarz
subTitle: Sita raises her son, Bihari, and his friend Amar as her own and the two treat each other like brothers. However, Amar's father is not too fond of Bihari, and he tries to create a rift between the two.

title: Naanu Matthu Gunda
subTitle: Shankar, an autorickshaw driver, adopts an abandoned dog and names it Gunda. However, his life turns upside down when his affection for the canine deepens.

title: God Tussi Great Ho
subTitle: When an anchor, Arun, who is down on his luck, blames God for his misfortunes, God decides to give him his powers for ten days. Soon chaos ensues when Arun decides to grant everyone's wishes.

title: Pralay the Destroyer
subTitle: Some thugs annihilate an entire family and flee the scene without facing any consequences. Years later, the universe balances the scales of justice through the sole survivor of the tragedy.

title: Naseeb Apna Apna
subTitle: A naive village girl marries the son of a domineering man. However, upon her arrival at his house in the city, she finds out that he is already married.

title: Saugandh
subTitle: Sarang, an evil landlord, kills Ganga's family. Years later, Shiva, Ganga's son, marries Chand, Sarang's daughter, to seek revenge from Sarang by destroying his ego.

title: Krantiveer
subTitle: Pratap, a gambler disowned by his family, comes under the care of a landlord named Laxminath. When corrupt forces lead to Laxminath's murder, Pratap seeks revenge.

title: Kohram
subTitle: Colonel Balbir Singh Sodhi assumes a disguise to unveil the true colours of Veer Bhadra Singh, a corrupt minister. Soon, Major Ajit teams up with him to execute the mission.

title: Afsana Dilwalon Ka
subTitle: A gifted singer, Banne Khan, falls in love with Saba. However, Titlibai, a woman who wants him to marry her daughter, invites him to stay at her house.

title: Saudagar
subTitle: Veer and Rajeshwar's friendship turns bitter and they embrace enmity. Years later, their respective grandchildren Vasu and Radha fall in love and decide to end their enmity.

title: Family of Thakurganj
subTitle: In a small rustic town in UP, two brothers, Nannu and Munnu, chose very different paths. While one chooses a life of crime, the other runs a coaching centre.

title: Phool Aur Kaante
subTitle: Love leads Ajay down a new path when he is expected to inherit his father's criminal empire, bringing along perils that could either tear their family apart or solidify their bond.

title: Loafer
subTitle: Ranjeet is a thief who works for Mr Singh. When they plan to steal precious jewellery, their enemy, Pratap, coerces Anju to spy on Ranjeet in order to kill him.

title: Aarzoo
subTitle: After her fiance, Vijay is killed in a crash, a pregnant Pooja agrees to marry Amar, her childhood friend. However, her life takes yet another turn when Vijay returns to her life.

title: Jigar
subTitle: Duryodhan, a wrestler, is Raju's friend, but due to a misunderstanding he rapes and kills Raju's sister. Raju later seeks Baba Thakur's help to train in fighting to avenge his sister's death.

title: Jis Desh Mein Ganga Rehta Hai
subTitle: Ganga, an innocent man, is raised by a foster couple in a village. When he is brought back to his family in the city, he struggles to fit into modern society.

title: Encounter Shankar
subTitle: Post his transfer to a village, an encounter specialist sets out to stop a crime boss who wants to build a power plant in the region despite strong public opposition.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Super Singh
subTitle: Super Singh lives with his mother in Canada and leads a carefree life. However, his life changes when he gains superpowers and has to return to save Punjab from the drug lords and corrupt politicians.

title: Badla Naag Ka
subTitle: A fearless man hurts a snake when it tries to attack his lover. Later, he tries to protect himself from the snake which is trying to exact its revenge.

title: Saajan Chale Sasural
subTitle: After Shyamsunder presumes that his first wife Pooja died in a flood, he marries Divya. When he learns that Pooja is alive, he has to juggle between his wives, keeping both his marriages a secret.

title: Shoorveer
subTitle: Siddharth, a fashion editor who hates horses, decides to venture into the world of horse racing to impress the girl of his dreams.

title: Andaaz
subTitle: After his sweetheart Kajal marries another man, Raj moves to Cape Town. He eventually agrees to marry Jiya but is shocked to find that she is Kajal's widowed sister-in-law.

title: Biwi No. 1
subTitle: Two adorable kids, a quirky mother-in-law and a happy-go-lucky friend help a heartbroken wife bring a straying husband back from the other woman's tangled embrace.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Hero Hindustani
subTitle: A young woman conspires with a man to fake a relationship, outsmarting her grandfather's plans to marry her off to a stranger.
